# .cursorrules

This file provides guidance to Cursor when working with code in this repository.

Read **`AGENTS.md`**. It is the canonical instructions file for AI assistants in this repo (rules of engagement, architecture, conventions). If present (maintainer-local archive), read **`MEMORY.md`** for current state; in the public repository it is absent and `ROADMAP.md` carries current status.

All documentation follows **ASD-STE100 Simplified Technical English** (see `AGENTS.md`, Style and Conventions).